Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:39.94,biaoti2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(348,285)}地球來客
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.93,0:00:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…車上有個奇怪的乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  聞到了  聞到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼辦法嘛  因為是你和我兩個人的分量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該沒那回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這身體是你的吧  只是你嘴饞罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功君  讓我來說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了攝取巴迪所需的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必須大量食用這個星球的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要表示成精確的能量單位的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說的不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.38,0:02:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托你們的福  我的生活已經亂七八糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅無視我的預定計劃  還在大庭廣眾之下在腦海中和我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去我不就要被人當成怪人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,實在抱歉  功君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是把你的生活放在第一位考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那以後就一直保持我的身體形態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊  這是不可能做得到的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是有抓捕罪犯的任務的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事情與我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是把我的身體毀壞掉的你不對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該也有過自己生活的權利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,確實功君說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把功君捲入我們的搜查在道德上也說不過去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是帝托  通情達理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是功君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不儘早抓到罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個星球也會面臨危險  這點希望你理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  身體不經我同意不能隨便用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  不是說好不能隨便變換身體的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還不是因為帝托你說的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊  做出那種約定都沒辦法正常搜查了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:04:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必須認真考慮與他共存的問題  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在與巴齊魯斯的戰鬥中  你應該察覺到自己能力的下降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你與體內的功君不能和睦共存
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去最壞的情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果發生精神融合導致我消失  這身體就讓給功君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是我把功君害死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼說這種自虐的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用更加發展的眼光去思考是什麼都解決不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說教到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你和功君的信賴關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼不喜歡我的話  你就當功君的伙伴好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你和功君的心能相連在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望能幫上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃好早餐可是健康之源哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飲食對健康很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今後為了你每天能夠舒適生活  我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是今天的午餐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了  功君  多了個能幹又聽話的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得你心情不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼  不是不能在大庭廣眾下說話的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早宮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題嗎  坐公車來上學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  身體狀況還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧  中杉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  你是千川同學對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,挺危險的  抓好吊環吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  中杉真是個大小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心跳加快了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發情了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰發情了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  沒…我自言自語
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川同學這人真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香小姐現在變得如此有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也為此感到高興
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這世上是存在奇蹟的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該去公司了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  把車開過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學這麼精神真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說發生事故時還挺擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事故好像挺嚴重的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,車好像都壓扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她有幸運女神眷顧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這便當很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你自己做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  當然啦  我一個人住嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得肚子餓  是在成長期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高中真好啊  墨田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  洋溢著夢想的青春歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當初我也為報道研的社團活動燃燒過激情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  室戶  我買就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs23}外星人是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,室戶啊  要寫的話就寫點正經的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可比正經的報道更能賺錢喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好賣的話就別到我這裡來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近不景氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  同是報道研出身  香里同學就很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\an7\fs20\frz270}{\fn@方正黑体_GBK}（特訊 新銳帝國TV再次選拔出人氣女主播）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,退後  退後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡不能進嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  職員請繞到後門進入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  那邊的不許進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真頭疼呀  那傢伙來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了  來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大人物登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,薩塔吉特·夏瑪朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  真田小姐剛進我們公司  可能還不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我們的重要合作人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,合作人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,守山先生  太小題大做了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是為表對夏瑪朗先生支持敝社的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:09:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不太喜歡這種迎接方式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平常點就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,採訪那個大人物的節目主持是真田小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可別惹他生氣哦  聽說最近還炒掉一個製片人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs21}（依露瑪的店）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基加消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝國電視台好像把他解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  基加住的公寓是找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情報雖然少  但還請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近紫苑的工作都沒什麼進展呐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等這個任務結束後  紫苑會好好工作給您賺錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實巴迪意外地很喜歡這個工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個事件結束後還能拿到休假
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那搜查結束後能讓紫苑上電視吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊  已經不用限制在公眾面前曝光了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就出CD加大宣傳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話肯定能大賺一筆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和紫苑兩人會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聞到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  說你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放…放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基加沒有回過公寓的跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發現多處巴齊魯斯留下的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  你在聽嗎  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在聽  我正在洗澡  通訊一律不接  通話結束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和功君沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:11:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基加那傢伙拿走的硫加是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是危險品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有多危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你連硫加是什麼東西都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼嘛  那種事就算不知道只要抓到基加他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是胡來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法啊  因為麥基烏斯警官也沒告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把硫加還來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道他們把硫加…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加弄丟了嗎  巴齊魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:38.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別叫那個名字  我是基加啊  基加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  基加先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你是特地跑來自我介紹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別耍我  我到這來是為了  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做什麼來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來你準備怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉那個阿留多人搜查官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且吃掉那傢伙就知道硫加的下落了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可真嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到硫加後要我帶到這裡來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎  按道理你應該要交給夏瑪朗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭夏瑪朗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那種傢伙我更喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感激  可是不好意思跟大家一塊吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  功君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥  你和帝托之間發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川同學  你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你找我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早宮  千川同學在這哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功君你真是的  找你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這可不行啊  忘帶運動服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下節是體育課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  你好好履行了和功君的約定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了  要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川  我會支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意旁人的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是可以的話就找我商量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟我倆是青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  中杉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那人真有趣  下次介紹一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,北村發的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不好  今天體育課是我倆負責體育用具的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉  我先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴齊魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是那個阿留多人的監護人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她果然在這
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  千川那傢伙吃便當要吃到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聞到了  聞到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  那個阿留多人就在那嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊  是你姐姐的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  對  我姐姐是個怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友也怪怪的  真是麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.29,0:14:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過真好啊  有個姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是獨生子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經這個時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川同學  下節是體育課
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得去換衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在一邊看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉  身體不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係  事實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有一天能和大家一起上體育課就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你得快點了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  抓錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喲  阿留多人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可騙不了我的鼻子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不想這個地球人被吃掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓我吃了你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快來讓我吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那女孩面前不能變換形態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就用你的身體了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想救那個女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  功君的身體肌肉力量太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微鍛煉一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這女孩看來是沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很可愛的女生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  現在發情可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會發情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就交換形態了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被基加抓到就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是把基加吞噬了的巴齊魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那他就是之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最怕那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點追上去的話又會被他逃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川到哪去了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙又一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  看見中杉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能逃進來的應該只有這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正好  這裡也不會被人看見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到了
